{
  "schema_version": "2.0",
  "name": "codex",
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "type": "gameplay",
  "required": false,
  "description": "Codex/encyclopedia plugin that tracks discovered knowledge entries across categories.",
  "dependencies": ["database", "core-blocks"],
  "prompt": {
    "position": "memory",
    "priority": 40,
    "template": "prompts/codex-context.md"
  },
  "capabilities": {},
  "blocks": {
    "codex_entry": {
      "instruction": "当玩家发现新知识、遭遇新怪物、获得新物品、到达新地点或了解到重要传说时，在回复末尾附加：\n```json:codex_entry\n{\"action\": \"unlock\", \"category\": \"monster\", \"entry_id\": \"goblin\", \"title\": \"哥布林\", \"content\": \"矮小的绿皮生物...\", \"tags\": [\"敌人\", \"弱小\"]}\n```\n规则：\n- action 为 unlock（首次发现）或 update（补充已有条目）\n- category 必须为以下之一：monster/item/location/lore/character\n- entry_id 为唯一标识符（英文小写，用连字符分隔）\n- content 为该条目的知识描述\n- tags 和 image_hint 为可选字段\n- 仅在玩家确实获得新知识时输出，不要重复已知信息",
      "schema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "action": { "type": "string", "enum": ["unlock", "update"] },
          "category": { "type": "string", "enum": ["monster", "item", "location", "lore", "character"] },
          "entry_id": { "type": "string" },
          "title": { "type": "string" },
          "content": { "type": "string" },
          "tags": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
          "image_hint": { "type": "string" }
        },
        "required": ["action", "category", "entry_id", "title", "content"]
      },
      "handler": {
        "actions": [
          { "type": "storage_write", "key": "codex-entries" },
          { "type": "emit_event", "event": "codex-unlocked" }
        ]
      },
      "ui": {
        "component": "custom",
        "renderer_name": "codex_entry"
      },
      "requires_response": false
    }
  },
  "events": {
    "emit": ["codex-unlocked"],
    "listen": []
  },
  "storage": {
    "keys": ["codex-entries"]
  },
  "permissions": {},
  "extensions": {
    "runtime_settings": {
      "settings": [
        {
          "key": "codex_detail",
          "type": "enum",
          "label": "Codex Detail Level",
          "description": "Level of detail in codex entry descriptions.",
          "default": "detailed",
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "brief",
              "label": "Brief",
              "i18n": { "zh": { "label": "简要" } }
            },
            {
              "value": "detailed",
              "label": "Detailed",
              "i18n": { "zh": { "label": "详细" } }
            }
          ],
          "affects": ["story"],
          "i18n": {
            "zh": {
              "label": "图鉴详细度",
              "description": "图鉴条目描述的详细程度。"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "i18n": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Codex",
      "description": "Track discovered knowledge entries including monsters, items, locations, lore, and characters."
    },
    "zh": {
      "name": "图鉴百科",
      "description": "记录玩家发现的知识条目，包括怪物、物品、地点、传说与角色。"
    }
  }
}
